  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCDOConflictProcessor
    Abstract superclass for ICDOConflictProcessors that only want to report a subset of possible application-level conflicts.
    AddedInSourceAndDetachedInTargetConflict
    Reported when a component is added on the source branch, but it references a component (either directly or indirectly) which was detached on the target branch.
    AddedInSourceAndTargetConflict
    Reported when components with the same domain key are added on both the source and the target branch.
    AddedInTargetAndDetachedInSourceConflict
    Reported when a component is added on the target branch, but it references a component (either directly or indirectly) which was detached on the source branch.
